Deadly Shot					KEY:Deadly Shot ~ Deeds			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.Deed	PRECLASS:1,Gunslinger=19	VISIBLE:YES		DEFINE:DeadlyShotSaveDC|0			SOURCEPAGE:p.5		DESC:When you confirm a critical hit against a living creature, you can spend 1 grit point to choose to deal normal damage, and the target must succeed at a Fortitude saving throw with a %1 DC. On a failed saving throw, the target dies. This is a death effect. Performing this deed does not allow you to regain grit from confirming a critical hit.|DeadlyShotSaveDC		BONUS:VAR|DeadlyShotSaveDC|10+(var("CLASSLEVEL=Gunslinger")/2)+DEX
